public interface Rollable extends Closeable
Interface for objects that need to take action on various intervals.

  • Method Details

    • roll

      void roll()
      Rolls selected object. Operations should be timely in nature to prevent Agent threads from blocking if internal implementations operate in that fashion.

    • isRolling

      boolean isRolling()
      True if this object is currently rolling, false otherwise. This method should be thread safe.
      Returns:
      true if this object is currently rolling; false otherwise
